org.usfirst.frc.team69.util.pid

Class PassivePIDController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.PIDController
      • org.usfirst.frc.team69.util.pid.PrefPIDController
        • org.usfirst.frc.team69.util.pid.PassivePIDController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.livewindow.LiveWindowSendable, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.PIDInterface, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Sendable

    public class PassivePIDController
extends PrefPIDController
    This class is a PrefPIDController with no output. This is useful if calculating the PID output is only part of calculating the outputs to actuators. Use PIDController.get() to check the last output value.
